      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, finely dice the <strong>remaining onion</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>shredded kale</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1665420612318-x200.jpg",
