            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tomato paste</strong>,<strong> Henderson's Relish</strong>,<strong> tomato ketchup </strong>and<strong> </strong>200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[320ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> to the pan</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 3-4 min or until the sauce has reduced to a thick gravy-like consistency – this is your<strong> curried tomato sauce</strong></p><p>Once thickened, remove the pan from the heat and set aside</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
