            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> to the <strong>shredded</strong> <strong>kale</strong> and massage it with clean hands so that it's evenly covered in oil</p><p>Once the sausages are cooked, remove the tray[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>from the oven and sprinkle over the <strong>kale</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 3-4 min or until the kale is cooked and slightly crispy – this is your <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>sausage</strong> <strong>tray bake</strong></p>",
