    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>curried tomato sauce</strong> to a low heat to reheat gently</p><p>Serve the <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>sausage</strong> <strong>tray bake</strong> with the<strong> curried tomato sauce</strong> drizzled all over</p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining curry powder </strong>– this is your <strong>German-style curried meat-free sausage tray bake</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
